@@ -16,10 +16,10 @@ CEC_RECEIVE, CEC_TRANSMIT - Receive or transmit a CEC message
 Synopsis
 ========
 
-.. c:function:: int ioctl( int fd, CEC_RECEIVE, struct cec_msg *argp )
+.. c:function:: int ioctl( int fd, CEC_RECEIVE, struct cec_msg \*argp )
